Although waist trimmers are a dime a dozen in the market, Getfitng is one of the brands that is being hailed by several public figures as effective and durable. And in recent months, it has become one of the most visible brands. According to Adekemi Oladipo, CEO, Getfit Technologies Limited, the positive reviews were no hype, but heartfelt appreciations coming from satisfied users who have gotten value for their money. “All Getfitng products are custom-made with technological driven materials that are of high quality; moreso, each of the product comes with secret tips, user instructions and manual,” she affirmed. Getfitng, Oladipo explained, was originally inspired to assist new mums to snap back to their pre-pregnancy sizes. “You know there is this general belief that women must lose their figures after childbirth,” she said, pointing out that the company has, however, decided to expand its scope to include “everyone who needs to look good and burn their belly fat, including men.” The last couple of years have witnessed the invasion of the market by different shades of waist trainers and trimmers. The development has elicited mixed reactions, which are prominently negative stories. One frequently hears complaints that some of the waist trainers don’t work, but Oladipo avowed that the Getfitng brand is above board and cannot be imputed with ineffectiveness.
“Getfitng products are waist and belly trimmers, not your conventional waist trainers, and they are very effective,” she submitted.
“We have thousands of testimonials from our customers across the world to back that up,” She further claimed.